"This file explains how to handle numbers"
"C (and our language) allows 3 types of numbers:"
" Octal, Hex, and Decimal (regular)"

" Octal numbers start with a 0 and use digits from 0-7:" 0777

" Hex numbers start with 0x and use 0-9 and a-f as the digits:" 0xFFFF

" Decimal numbers are regular numbers!" 12345
